The following episode:
Vegeta: Your old tricks no longer have any effect on me. You see, I've tapped into a power far greater than any this world has ever seen: DREADLOCK…CARNIVAL!
*proceeds to get his ass kicked in two minutes by Merged Chris Rock*

Vegeta: H-how!? I put all my power behind that attack! There's no way you could have survived that!
Goku Chris Rock: I got paid $8 million to say "AFRO CIRCUS!" for twenty fucking minutes. I. Am. Invincible.
